OL,6,FAt 6.26am on 30 May 2025, Richens
OL,7,Fcalled police from his home to say he
OL,8,Fhad killed a woman.
OL,10,FOfficers and South Central Ambulance
OL,11,FService crew went to the scene but
OL,12,Fdespite efforts to save Ms Vaughan,
OL,13,Fthe 40-year-old from Abingdon, died at
OL,14,Fthe scene.
OL,16,FRichens was arrested on the same day
OL,17,Fand charged the day after.
