OL,3,CMan told police he'll 'miss Grand
OL,4,CTheft Auto' after murdering ex-partner
OL,6,FFollowing his arrest, Richens told
OL,7,Fofficers: "I'm going to miss GTA and
OL,8,Fthat", before adding "Oh, I'm going to
OL,9,Fget life".
OL,11,FSenior investigating officer Detective
OL,12,FChief Inspector Stuart May said: "My
OL,13,Fthoughts remain with Rachael Vaughan's
OL,14,Ffamily and with everyone who loved her
OL,15,Fas they continue to face what is an
OL,16,Funimaginable loss.
OL,18,F"Rachael was taken from them in the
OL,19,Fvery place she should have felt safest
OL,20,F- her own home.
