OL,6,F"Robert Richens' actions were
OL,7,Fheartless. He left Rachael alone in
OL,8,Fher house, made no attempt to help her
OL,9,For seek medical attention and he only
OL,10,Fcontacted police when he had nowhere
OL,11,Felse to turn.
OL,13,F"Today's sentence means that Richens
OL,14,Fwill now face the consequences of his
OL,15,Fmerciless actions."
